40|$|This article {{analyzes}} {{the owners of}} public property: {{the state and the}} territorial administrative units. The article analyzes various theories about the quality in which the State exercising the right of public property (independently of the a <b>legal</b> <b>person,</b> based on the national sovereignty or as a <b>public</b> law <b>legal</b> <b>person).</b> Similar is analyzed the quality in which the administrative-territorial unit exercises the right of public property. In this article are analyzed also the meanings of the term "administrative territorial unit"...|$|R
